msg: backport.pl: Teach it how to skip entries it prompted for in a previous run.
Currently only used in interactive mode.
(parse_entry): Store a digest of the entry in the entry.
(vote): Change signature, set state if the vote or approval went through.
(handle_entry): Change signature, skip entries in state, add entries to state
on 'N' (but not on unrecognized keypresses such as 'x').
(main): Read state, pass it in calls.
